{"type":null,"faqId":43938,"title":"为什么手机上不了4G？","answer":"<html>\n<head>\n<META http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n<style type=\"text/css\">.b1{white-space-collapsing:preserve;}\n.d1{margin: 1.18125in 0.7875in 1.18125in 0.7875in;}\n.s1{color:black;}\n.p1{margin-left:0.70902777in;margin-top:0.11111111in;margin-bottom:0.11111111in;text-align:start;hyphenate:auto;font-family:微软雅黑;font-size:10pt;}\n</style>\n</head>\n<body class=\"b1\">\n<div  >\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">1. 需要去营业厅更换专用手机卡。如果是更换套餐，一般要到下月才生效。放在其他手机上，如果也不能用4G，基本可以确认是卡的问题。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">2. 确认打开手机4G开关。在设置中，网络模式设置为4G/3G/2G模式。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">3. 确认下当地是否有4G信号覆盖。建议把卡放在其他手机上尝试。如果有问题，建议打运营商客服反馈。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">4. 注意购买的手机支持4G的情况。一般来说，定制版本的手机都只支持本运营商的4G业务，比如电信定制版本就只支持电信4G网，移动定制版本就只支持移动4G网。双卡手机的副卡，只能用2G业务。</span>\n</p>\n<p  >\n<span class=\"s1\">5. 在部分地区（深圳）如果4G套餐流量用完，4G网会注册不上。建议暂时关闭4G。</span>\n</p>\n</div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","faqTypeId":138,"faqType":"网络与数据共享","useful":0,"unUseful":0,"languageId":2,"languageName":"zh_cn","faqCode":"9439","faqTypeCode":"Handsets-Network-Data-sharing","isTop":"0","moduleCode":"faq","productId":null,"productCode":null,"postDate":1442399726000,"seriesProductName":"CRR-CL10,CRR-TL10,CRR-UL10","visitedTimes":23,"isUsefulFlag":null,"score":0,"times":0,"imageList":null,"displayType":"text","justView":"0","fileName":null,"filePath":null,"imagePath":null,"imageName":null,"productIdList":null,"curPage":null,"pageSize":null,"siteCode":null,"statusFlag":"Publish","returnCode":0,"totalRows":null,"keywords":"G","avgScore":0.0,"createDate":null,"totalPages":null}